edu.umn.nlpengine

Class Label

  • edu.umn.nlpengine.Label
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TextRange

    public class Label
implements TextRange

    A labeled element in text.

    Implementation specification

    Labels should be immutable after construction, equals should be consistent with TextRange.locationEquals (returning true iff TextRange.locationEquals returns true), Comparable should be consistent with TextRange.compareLocation (returning 0 iff compareLocation returns 0, and having ordering first determined by TextRange.compareLocation then by any other factors). Kotlin data classes are an excellent choice for implementations of label.

    See Also:
    TextRange.locationEquals, TextRange.locationEquals, Comparable, TextRange.compareLocation, TextRange.compareLocation
